         <notesStmt>
            <note type="project" target="dat1">This is a partial draft of the poem published as "The Mississippi at Midnight" on March 6, 1848, in the <hi rend="italic">New Orleans Daily Crescent</hi>. A revised version of the poem, titled "Sailing the Mississippi at Midnight," was later included in <hi rend="italic">Specimen Days &amp; Collect</hi> (1882–3). Whitman left for New Orleans in February, 1848, so this manuscript was almost certainly written in that month.</note>
